le="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;设置机器人的工具&lt;/strong&gt;从未如此简单。像 OpenClaw 这样的开源平台允许想要选股的人通过 WhatsApp 和 Telegram 等消息应用程序与他们的人工智能代理交谈。但风险也是存在的， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/JRfm4KpCR5F46ABvp5re_N_WjwrjuJ3iU_2Hex_6ZApifQfik6EBG9xmjsBDozct6vi3lvJ7MGdLmdfq7t8T3CO0lgGu_rmHDCeaS8P7y3Yp7rJ8OcRd03r3fnoEIN5v8m7mXoO-ORId-owIOSz5_WzX-pBM55cDdCNmcnpw5MnbqPxnRd7lL686nNuE0juHdQJshrIKQoD3hVJJup4XNZWR2YtkuDuAQ8-1ZdBXmjXc0yuSVUJfcqq-x1dykGeLHY4pYB9qL9-zYM-EaSFXLLtrNn_YxO7mELH1blirEwDQdlJjfnq_4A11hnLrvmfqlDMN0_xBbxYYKia9mMJ3d55hNacf-7sL0gQ16K92HKYputKszGGKejxrCOFpWZWztUtVnVOVzuhe3gukXvRFnDAcIEMbXPMEwfCre2q-A6yuo0Zw64QpyBk7Z7mV9zddRTA6V_aOHOOdtcT0JTpS90qe1R33guss-hdc2T6aSiTOnngj66cVEuvsRAArzR8ou_Uz9FyVfNtO9N0-9PG266gGvFlZlc4LdWG9iQJqaBhFunXwhvs/o1gnC3lM5gbU6VPHnpVpd_ibrqbZqpy_/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="OpenClaw - 人工智能奇迹还是网络安全噩梦？"&gt;黑客攻击只是其中之一&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;还有炒作。&lt;/strong&gt;还记得 2021 年的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/t3B4lrlZXe0vb8Q8yAsf0AJp3fs4UyAyYgVg40oWIap9jYzBT9EKybrZy0jcJYjls7zgXYmb1x6t87yT4baHTTKWVHRCQtjKTGHlxYQ33iq8SPPJl6qEn8IskkYI_g5GuGmsAohaQe0zsffs9wwBq9LO1BM2SwB-dWIhyecGhlL2bVF34KdF9Dv5amTrZsHXS9leIqnfzY4e6A4KZjTuea49blvLx_C32DymAR8jGN0YPTio488_q9oJvLQfPMbtJx6RVsNmKFY88GpGkoDicOAN6d0hY9DxuPpBk_MgqMuZjFX3mdbW30rGDMFUxDQpnE3h2hU1HHlfk25F4VJHQ2naJBrwO60qCaoP5h7IjOsscBxDwSu3rExU1lkZqkNWHFzm1cwzqUVRR1Os4yer4mv_yB_zP1Y7eN4zOntJi7lLI0JIRjKB8NH9GOZ3bIS2j3LK4_WgavrA_pzIvdvQX6eaXjfnFdHYjqr_dD7NW9SF0C8JBAJ11WxobDgSqVRippIUsBwcaqcaxKf78UgyXvnfP7rGow/by1iDHqA4ngf9j8rccSdkXNkkODW5pEt/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank" title="Robinhood 依靠婴儿和 401(k)